    <string name="help_catalog_desc">Catalog lets you access all your clothes in a list like view and <b>filter</b> them by some fields. If you click any of the list items it will show you all its details. On <b>long click</b> a contextual menu will appear to let you edit or remove the selected cloth</string>
    <string name="help_combinator_desc">The combinator lets you make your own combinations and store them.</string>
    <string name="help_ic_combinator">Save combination</string>
    <string name="help_combinations_desc">This screen shows you your saved combinations in a list like view, you can select any of them to check it out clearly on the combinator.</string>
